Mathilde Seigner https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathilde_Seigner 0 Mathilde Seigner (born 17 January 1968) is a French actress. Seigner was born in Paris, France. She is the granddaughter of actor Louis Seigner (1903-1991). Seigner is the sister of Emmanuelle Seigner and a niece of Françoise Seigner.
